    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture or style of a subgroup of the Fulbe African people living in the Futa Toro region of northern Senegal and southern Mauritania.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
